Field Discovery			SORTKEY:Class Feature 05a		KEY:Alchemist Class Feature ~ Field Discovery			SOURCEPAGE:p.74	CATEGORY:Class Feature	TYPE:Alchemist Class Feature.Class Feature.Display											DESC:You learn a special discovery depending on your field.	DESC:Bomber: When using advanced alchemy to make bombs during your daily preparations, you can use a batch of reagents to create any three bombs instead of just two of the same bomb.|PREVAREQ:AlchemistBomber,1	DESC:Chirurgeon: When using advanced alchemy to make elixirs of life during your daily preparations, you can create three elixirs with each batch of reagents instead of two.|PREVAREQ:AlchemistChirurgeon,1	DESC:Mutagenist: When using advanced alchemy to make mutagens during your daily preparations, you can use a batch of reagents to create any three mutagens instead of just two of the same mutagen.|PREVAREQ:AlchemistMutagenist,1
