Bomber				SORTKEY:Alchemist Class Feature 1d2	KEY:Alchemist Class Feature ~ Research Field ~ Bomber		SOURCEPAGE:p.73	CATEGORY:Class Feature	TYPE:Alchemist Class Feature.Class Feature.Display.Alchemist Research Field	DEFINE:AlchemistBomber|0		DESC:You specialize in explosions and other violent alchemical reactions. You start with the formulas for two 1st-level alchemical bombs in your formula book, in addition to your other formulas. When throwing an alchemical bomb with the splash trait, you can deal splash damage to only your primary target instead of the usual splash area.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																				BONUS:VAR|AlchemistBomber|1|TYPE=Boolean
Chirurgeon				SORTKEY:Alchemist Class Feature 1d2	KEY:Alchemist Class Feature ~ Research Field ~ Chirurgeon	SOURCEPAGE:p.73	CATEGORY:Class Feature	TYPE:Alchemist Class Feature.Class Feature.Display.Alchemist Research Field	DEFINE:AlchemistChirurgeon|0		DESC:You concentrate on healing others with alchemy. You start with the formulas for two of the following in your formula book, in addition to your other formulas: lesser antidote, lesser antiplague, or lesser elixir of life. As long as your proficiency rank in Medicine is trained or better, you can attempt a Crafting check instead of a Medicine check for any of Medicine's untrained and trained uses.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																									BONUS:VAR|AlchemistChirurgeon|1|TYPE=Boolean
