Bard Weapon Expertise	SORTKEY:Class Feature 11a	KEY:Bard Class Feature ~ Bard Weapon Expertise	SOURCEPAGE:p.99	CATEGORY:Class Feature	TYPE:Bard Class Feature.Class Feature.Display	DESC:You have become thoroughly adept with bardic weapons. You gain expert proficiency in simple weapons, plus the longsword, rapier, sap, shortbow, shortsword, and whip. When you critically succeed at an attack roll using one of these weapons while one of your compositions is active, you apply the critical specialization effect for that weapon.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																														ASPECT:Level|11th
