Adamantine Strikes 17th			KEY:Monk Class Feature ~ Adamantine Strikes			SOURCEPAGE:p.158	CATEGORY:Class Feature	TYPE:Monk Class Feature.Class Feature.Display			DESC:When you focus your will into your limbs, your blows are as unyielding as the hardest of metals. Your unarmed attacks are treated as adamantine.
